	default 6
	range 0 11 if STM32_HAVE_IP_TIMERS_V2
	range 0 7 if !STM32_HAVE_IP_TIMERS_V2
	---help---
		Specifies the channel mode. See enum stm32_pwm_chanmode_e in stm32_pwm.h.

